title: Regular Show
description:
Written by Jon Bershad and Avery Monsen

Starring Lisa Kleinman, Langan Kingsley, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, James McCarthy, Kelly Hudson, Dan Hodapp, Avery Monsen, Jonathan Marballi.

Directed by John Flynn.
Piano by Eric Gersen.

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, August 13, 2012.

Filmed by Alex Aden.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
